		"description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 21\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><strong>Requirement: </strong>Unused spell slot of 3rd level or higher or at least 5 unspent spell points, spell from the conjuration school available to cast.</p>\n<p>You call upon your magical abilities to pass through an enemy&rsquo;s defenses as if they were not there.</p>\n<p>You make a single weapon attack against a target, with a +20 bonus to hit. This attack requires such intense focus that it cannot be augmented via other means such as a herald&rsquo;s Divine Smite, a rogue's Sneak Attack, or any other spell or effect that would add additional effects to the attack. The attack cannot land a critical hit.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
